<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link rel="icon" href="/img/icon.ico"/>
    <title>log in</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/signup.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: center;">
    <form action="/signup" method="POST" class="signup-box">
        <h2>Sign up</h2>
        <div>닉네임 : <input type="text" name="nickname" placeholder="nickname" maxlength="7" minlength="1"></div>
        <div>아이디 : <input type="text" name="id" placeholder="영어, 숫자만 사용가능" pattern="[A-Za-z0-9]+" title="아이디는 영어와 숫자만 사용 가능합니다." maxlength="20" minlength="3"></div>
        <div>비밀번호 : <input type="password" name="pw" placeholder="Password" maxlength="20" minlength="3"></div>
        <button type="submit" style="margin-top: 5px;">Sign up</button>
    </form>
    <div>이미 계정이 있나요? <a href="/login"> 로그인 하러가기</a></div>
</body>
</html>
